# PulseVerse Visual System (mandatory)

Full spec: **`docs/UI_VISION.md`** § *PulseVerse Visual System*. Use **`theme/`** + shared primitives; extend tokens before new magic values.

## Brand & look

- **Premium, futuristic, polished, cinematic** — luxury dark; **healthcare-social, elevated** (not sterile).
- **Neon glass — restrained, expensive.** Navy/near-black **layered** bases; **cyan / teal / electric blue** accents; **gold** for featured / legendary / verified only where appropriate.
- **Never** flat black; **never** noisy FX. Backgrounds = **rich, dimensional** (gradient + subtle vertical/radial texture); optional **slow** streaks/particles if animated.

## Cards (major)

- Fill band ~ **`rgba(12,18,32,0.82)` → `rgba(18,26,44,0.92)`**; **blur** when possible.
- **Radius 20–28px**; **~1px** cyan-blue **low-opacity** border.
- **Layered shadow** + **faint cyan outer glow only** where hierarchy needs it — interior softly **lit**, not flat.

## Glass / glow

- **Subtle** glass — not frosted overload. **No** thick bright rings on everything.
- **Strong glow:** primary CTAs, **featured** cards, **active** tabs, **premium** icons.
- **Soft / none:** secondary UI.

## Buttons

- **Primary:** cyan → electric-blue gradient, **white** text, pill or rounded rect, **soft halo + inner highlight**; press = slightly **darker**, glow **tighter**.
- **Secondary:** dark glass, subtle border, cyan/white text, **minimal** glow.
- **Danger / low emphasis:** **subdued**.

## Type & space

- Strict **hierarchy:** screen title → section → card title → muted meta. **No** cramped text; meta **never** fights titles.
- **Generous editorial rhythm**; consistent scale — **no** edge-to-edge packs; **no** crowded chip rows.

## Chips & icons

- **Compact premium capsules**; rarity stands out; supporting chips stay **quiet**.
- Icons: **clean outlined / soft filled**, **one** style; glow **active-only**; not cartoon.

## Featured heroes

**Stronger** light + gradient than default cards; **spotlight** behind hero object; **clear CTA**; **stronger** badges; **flagship drop** depth.

## Bottom nav

**Darker glass** bar; **subtle** active-tab glow; **premium** center action if used; precise modern icons.

## Do not

Flat generic cards; outline/blur/glow **overuse**; gaming neon; childish gradients; cramming.

## Goal & implementation

Screens = **premium luxury social** + **cinematic neon-glass**. Compose **background → glass/veil → content**; build **reusable** card/button patterns. Document exceptions in `docs/UI_VISION.md`.
